        {
          "id": 3,
          "title": "3. Create CRUD operations for profiles (Create, Read, Update, Delete)",
          "description": "Implement comprehensive database operations for managing Analysis Profiles with proper validation and error handling.",
          "details": "1. Create a ProfileRepository class with the following methods:\\n   - create_profile(profile): Insert a new profile with validation [DONE]\\n   - get_profile_by_id(id): Retrieve a profile by its unique ID [DONE]\\n   - get_profile_by_name(name): Retrieve a profile by name [DONE]\\n   - get_all_profiles(filters=None): Retrieve all profiles with optional filtering [DONE]\\n   - update_profile(profile): Update an existing profile [DONE]\\n   - delete_profile(id): Remove a profile from storage [DONE]\\n2. Implement optimistic locking to prevent concurrent modification issues [Partially Done in update]\\n3. Add comprehensive error handling with specific exceptions [DONE]\\n4. Include transaction support to ensure data consistency [DONE in create/update/delete]\\n5. Implement logging for all operations with appropriate detail levels [DONE]\\n6. Add performance metrics collection [TODO]\\n7. Ensure thread safety for all operations [TODO - basic check_same_thread=False used]\\n8. Implement pagination for retrieving large sets of profiles [DONE in get_all]\\n\\n<info added on 2025-05-04T02:37:58.801Z>\\n... (rest of details) ...\\n</info added on 2025-05-05T14:22:31.801Z>",
